eed_on_going_public_at":"2023-11-29T21:40:42.120Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"In Django versions before 4.2.7, 4.1.13, and 3.2.23, I sent a POST request to the admin login page using Burp Suite, editing the request to send over 1 million invalid unicode characters to my local  web server running Django. (I used: \"¾\")\nAfter submitting, a single request took 4.4 seconds on average.\nWhen I sent 20 concurrent requests, then I got 60 second wait times, and 504 gateway timeout errors on my machine.\n{F2871465}\nNormal ascii characters don't do this and the page loads instantly.\n\n## Impact\n\nDenial of Service anywhere a form contains a UsernameField that checks for errors.","bounty_amount":"2540.0","formatted_bounty":"$2,540","weakness":{"id":48,"name":"Uncontrolled Resource Consumption"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":2871465,"file_name":"504-gateway-timeout.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/jsi4cbamvwyoyzjkizdp59lx86lb?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22504-gateway-timeout.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27504-gateway-timeout.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQSNO7E6PL%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T072900Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECcaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIGh%2F1yGCzYbilHKJgKv7zwKw4njvegTCqGOqHrZ2zFjNAiAtwhUwrtY8N2r7rnFNnaOuIHaWcMl8cxvlDcdW9%2F0Fsiq7BQjw%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMYfQ8VyYhvJqNT7sWKo8FFtojwydBtrKaMqWAYor6FYyhw3tBQGuCeswHBF78kKMPxGeCibg8S7k%2B7Ng%2FU5IgMHWGbxP30o8hHcmh3XKaioTReTDo7UKYGeoc2S8ggIAnXswKyI6AgeB6zVZ1RTFYIhgHdIIaAnxATC40POAsCkAoEQwFC0j7DDxvCJz139iwT01wvOQzClDaIMMBNS6hvkRENg2ZbURJbmSVNBR9vasffKh%2BQ6xx8XH7e6fPc5hnZBE5MecHxbS5tmybL5Kw%2FXR2g4ncEZkWizIRcj7